description: Today I wanted to tap some cute and tiny ass. So I´ve had to look harder to find one. Considering the cold weather outside it wasn´t really a pleasant search. But as you all know me, I never give up. Walked all the way to Namesti Miru until I´ve found what I was looking for. Hardly 170cm, cute and kinda scared young fella was luckily willing to get interviewed. He didn´t have a proper job nor education. It was getting better and better. I knew that he will go for some good extra cash in his pocket. Even tough he said that he is a show off, it was impossible to persuade him to do something in public. So I´ve just shown him the money and proposed to rent a hotel room, where he can show me what I wanted. He was a complete fulfillment of all my today´s desires.
title: Czech Hunter 179
